SWERVIN' MERVIN'
---------------

A recreation of 80's-style pseudo-3D arcade racing games.

Accelleration and steering are (well, will be) performed by integrating with a LEAP Motion Controller.


CREDITS
  * Jake at codeincomplete.com and Lou at extentofthejam.com for their fantastic articles on the subject.
  * My beautiful girlfriend, Mel, for all of the original pixel art.
